# Jules (Google's coding agent) — keeps its workspace droppings out of the repo
.jules/

# Local-only golden fixtures — dev-machine images for richer regression
# coverage that don't belong in the public repo (personal photos, licensed
# stock, etc.). Both golden harnesses walk this dir as a second fixture root
# alongside `golden_data/` and apply the same bootstrap/verify rules.
crates/prunr-core/tests/golden_data_local/

# Triptych output from `cargo xtask render-golden-diff` — reviewer artifacts,
# not committed. The actual goldens live under `tests/golden_data/`; this
# directory just holds the visual `<before|after|diff>` PNGs used to inspect
# math-changing refactors before commit.
/golden-diffs/
